title: Gym booking and account system
desc: A C# based application for a Gym
about:
This project was created for my graded unit in my final year of college for my HND, the project brief was to create a website for a Gym that incorporated accounts, a booking system, account system and an admin panel.

The project achieved an A for the graded unit, the project taught me a lot about time management and working within the agile development methodology.

My time at college and projects such as my graded unit provided me with a general idea of what it's like to work within the software development industry and provided me with a good practical knowledge of development.
